Package: picar
Title: Pica Data Import (via Catmandu) and Analysis
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Donatus Herre <mail@herre.io> [aut, cre]"
Description: Import Pica data via Catmandu command line interface from different
    SRU interfaces and store content parsed as picaxml to local json files.
    Read these files via jsonlite to extract specific pica tags of items and perform
    further bibliographic analysis based on that. Focus lies on german library
    cataloging formats from GBV union and the German National Library.
License: file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite
SystemRequirements: Perl, Catmandu::SRU, Catmandu::PICA
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
